9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"My First Girlfriend is a Gal | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Junichi Hashiba is nearing the end of high school and going into panic mode. His time here has not gone as expected: he has no girlfriend and worse yet—he’s still a virgin! Desperate to experience the big ‘first,’ his friends pressure him to approach the gyaru—a fashionable and boy-crazy gal—Yukana Yame for a good time. But his first mistake was thinking this gal would be an easy one!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation)"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149531/my-first-girlfriend-is-a-gal"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"My First Girlfriend is a Gal"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Junichi Hashiba is nearing the end of high school and going into panic mode. His time here has not gone as expected: he has no girlfriend and worse yet—he’s still a virgin! Desperate to experience the big ‘first,’ his friends pressure him to approach the gyaru—a fashionable and boy-crazy gal—Yukana Yame for a good time. But his first mistake was thinking this gal would be an easy one!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation)"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149531/my-first-girlfriend-is-a-gal"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx97863-79AXrUZ7VQa5.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.tv_show"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"My First Girlfriend is a Gal"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","con